column2: select a.objID,a.ra,a.dec,c.logMass,c.z  from PhotoObj as a, Photoz as b, stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as c, SpecPhotoAll as d where a.type = # and a.objID = b.objID and c.specObjID=a.specObjID and a.specObjID = d.specObjID   and c.fiberID = d.fiberID and c.plate = d.plate and c.MJD = d.mjd    and abs(c.z*#-#)<# and c.logMass># and abs(a.ra-#)<#   and abs(a.dec-#)<# and abs(b.z-c.z)<#
